<p>
	A juicy, fruity accord of Cranberries and zesty Lime with supporting fruity notes of Strawberry, Raspberry, Plum, Peach, Apple and Cassis with hints of White Flowers on a woody base<br />
	The candle is hand crafted using pure essential oils and will burn for approximately 35 hours.</p>
<p>
	When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended.</p>
